{"tid":1469941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈同好俾仇恨支配大家！一中計就萬劫不復同失民心！","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T01:06:09.000Z","uid":47496,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2847c380ce53414a80c6dc926189d73fc79b39c","tid":1469941,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:39:42.000Z","msg":"大家唔好中黑警計<br />\n黑警每日放返啲重傷義士<br />\n擺到明係惡意挑起勇武仇恨心理<br />\n繼而分化緊和理非<br />\n佢哋嘅目的只有一樣：學共產黨搞分化令抗爭者失民心<br />\n千萬唔好俾仇恨心理支配大家嘅理性<br />\n一有仇恨心理就會中哂計<br />\n黑警只會將來清算同等佢哋有報應！<br />\n<br />\n我苦苦哀求各位要冷靜同理性呀<br />\n你復仇心咁勁同黑警同黑社會有咩分別呀？<br />\n大家嘅五大訴求先係主要目的呀！<br />\n唔好俾班仆街分化大家呢兩個月得來不易嘅團結精神呀！<br />\n求求大家<br />\n我真係好想喊！"},{"pid":"d078cd174cba9f09d5ff82d54a126fe27c82de3a","tid":1469941,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:42:23.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19750e56f42dd1e1d6bd9f8613a7f063cdd02db","tid":1469941,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:44:42.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85214dba2f8b718cdf0cae58c4350bf52a1d905f","tid":1469941,"uid":190700,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVxLwho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVxLwho.jpg&h=415b935b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKH32ot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKH32ot.jpg&h=5e099b86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DYUh6P8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDYUh6P8.jpg&h=8cec500b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1df45eba3b288de27140c8a793573b86ba57272c","tid":1469941,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:50:39.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deab42a7f352e110291fd1d753f5fb09a179e966","tid":1469941,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6085112f6859466c3a62f04174c1604d768a7343","tid":1469941,"uid":281454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:06:51.000Z","msg":"8/13 中曬班老狐狸計，又設局s想民意逆轉<br />\n一、扮取消機<br />\n政府將旅客矛頭直指示威者<br />\nT1塞左離境係原罪，對住旅客、記者冇禮<br />\n唔該見到旅客幫佢地到T2登機，解答佢哋疑惑<br />\n更加fake曬冇登機的旅客，當no show 冇得 claim保險！表面上取消航班一面煽動唔俾旅客走，查實入到去係有得飛。<br />\n二、公安扮示威者<br />\nTrump Trump 唔係空穴來風，有人想等First Blood之後港版6 4 ,點解仲有人煽動打死狗？勿忘初心，我地唔係反社會，而且鬼係捉唔曬，請將焦點放在五大訴求<br />\n三、扮記者<br />\n大家在外國記者表現左稍為暴力一面，好彩冇first blood ,官媒都可以抹黑運動,局中局，而家無打死但佢係官媒既記者，國家體面與他報告的第一身被虐感受，做鬼點會帶藍絲衫及証件，希望前線保持克制冷靜，致勝的關鍵是獨立思考！<br />\n四、派鬼做show搞分化<br />\n依家唔係分化割席時候！<br />\n大家做得不完美<br />\n但可接受<br />\n要改善！"},{"pid":"ce856b5174e92bcd5a3a7dbaeccb178850c67705","tid":1469941,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fa1e95fd20e101d00829f64c00d161326a1911","tid":1469941,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28eb03e19a1413eaa0037041edea8a2888fca6d","tid":1469941,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f07f9060187a4850a86c4371ba4beef327238a5","tid":1469941,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/